Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.11,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Kurahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:33.97,Series_Title,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Run with the Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.34,Loop_01:50(Ep 13),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Shirakaba Loop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:56.51,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied running \Nwith the friends you finally made?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.42,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied holding hands and\Nrunning around with your little friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:06.78,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:31.38,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,See? You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:35.88,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You're always ruining someone else's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.34,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You don't see your teammates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.09,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:42.30,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you're just naturally talented,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:46.47,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,but if you think you alone will\Nmanage somehow, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.48,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.77,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:55.93,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.49,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:10.77,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.13,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.33,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Get your stuff on the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.38,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:30.99,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you just how serious\Nwe are at the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.42,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:39.86,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You first-years will be too busy\Nwith chores to watch the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.84,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Start by becoming regulars on your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:44.91,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:57.34,Ep_title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,And Then Start Running
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:10.31,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Your time hasn't even improved by ten seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.57,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of training have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:14.40,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.81,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a scholarship student?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:20.20,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Your only option is to do well at running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.11,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Go run ten more kilometers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.03,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.84,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.16,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Results are everything for runners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.38,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow any weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:39.82,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.91,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Kurahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.15,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kurahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.13,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,These men are prefectural officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.77,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,You won with a huge lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.77,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.72,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,You must be a top runner nationally, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.32,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,You can really see the results\Nof your coaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:20.51,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just blessed with talented runners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.60,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking forward to this year's\Nprefectural and national races.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.55,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:31.68,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they want me to speak\Nat a party about fostering athletes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:35.07,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked the coaches to manage\Nyour training schedule, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:35.98,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:39.31,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to what you've achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:43.04,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't walk so slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.19,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Look sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.90,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Don't damage Sendai Josei High School's dignity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.89,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be doing high-altitude training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.49,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to enjoy the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.53,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Seems gentle. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.33,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.34,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,The ground seems like \Nit'll be gentle on our knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.85,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Your leg hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.27,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you come up with a better excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:29.86,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has an injury or two\Nthey're working through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.18,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Runners improve their times despite them. Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.03,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.73,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be cutting everyone who doesn't do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.26,main,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.66,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.67,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. He's a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:48.81,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him he only needs\Nto try when he's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.20,main,KOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.31,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,He won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.52,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's a scholarship student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.14,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.61,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:20.65,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever suffered an injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.85,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.51,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.03,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:42.35,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.21,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.67,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,I see meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.40,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Those bags are full of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:55.37,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cook dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.93,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.33,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.62,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're on bathroom duty tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.98,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.03,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Quit surrounding Hana, you sweaty pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.45,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.11,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a little soon for you to be tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.70,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.03,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:33.74,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,My special crunchy liver and leek\Nstir fry contains tons of vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.70,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.45,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. They're making me feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.66,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to quit the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.55,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:53.49,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't be useful here,\Nyou won't be useful anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.49,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Your life will be decided here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:59.34,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand that? Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.06,flashback,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.98,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how fast you were in the boonies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.52,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,but here we coach based on years of theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:12.03,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't keep up, it's because\Nyou're not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.36,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.89,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.13,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.06,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:22.56,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Imagine you're racing for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.33,flashback,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.42,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you're representing\Na prestigious school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.45,flashback,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.12,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Leave behind those who can't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.50,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.49,flashback,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.34,Crumpled_paper_0937(Ep 13),,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:41.82,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,You can't handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.74,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,This year... This time,\NI don't think I'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:46.81,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,But by next year—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.15,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,You can't close the gap that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:55.58,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's pouring their blood,\Nsweat, and tears into practice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:58.15,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,every day while you're resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.24,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:02.16,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,The team will manage without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.56,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Get yourself healed up and find a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:19.52,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm here on a track scholarship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:23.28,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,If I quit the team, I won't have anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.77,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me run! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:26.99,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.15,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.20,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,It's time. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.38,flashback,CAPTAIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. To the track!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.74,flashback,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.41,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please let me back on the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:46.14,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I got injured! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.74,flashback,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.76,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,I only have time for students who can run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:03.43,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck. You have my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.97,flashback,COACH,0000,0000,0000,,Kurahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.06,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.72,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:47.63,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:52.57,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.47,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,He asked you to lead Group B since\Nwe're splitting into two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.38,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,Quit spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.75,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.45,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You must be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.85,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I heated up some milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.86,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.11,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a waste not to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.58,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.40,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,About me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:55.71,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:13:00.81,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,You knew the morning\Nafter I first stayed at Aotake
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.40,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,that I was from Sendai Josei High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.14,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.99,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:14.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,A quick search online revealed\Njust how good a runner you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.60,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That you were a nationally top-ranked\Nrunner by your second year,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.39,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,and that your records suddenly\Nstopped the spring of your third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.32,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.69,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There was no need for me \Nto investigate any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.10,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cause the team any more trouble\Nthan I have already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.08,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:46.74,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,When that reporter spoke to me, \NI felt like I had woken up from a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.39,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I realized no matter\Nhow far I run, I'm still me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.92,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.79,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.73,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to talk, why not tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:01.73,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.67,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, we're still us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.79,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're still awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:12.36,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you had to bathe last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.76,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Was the bath dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:14.96,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.94,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You cleaned it again for me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.52,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.75,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're that considerate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.72,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki told me to use my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.89,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Your seniors can teach you\Nall kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:28.68,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.54,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.42,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:35.10,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? I wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:39.31,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I don't. Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:44.14,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the night sky was just so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.93,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:47.72,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.70,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are mad pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.37,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.07,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.26,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,You'll wake the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.54,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Hana. A shooting star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.24,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:14.33,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I hated my high school track team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:20.06,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,My coach's methods,\Nthe stuffy air of that club room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.60,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I hated it so much, it made me want to puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:28.18,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I broke my coach's nose,\Nlost my college recommendation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.54,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,and quit the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:35.73,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Since the school wanted to keep it quiet,\Nthey imposed restrictions on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.06,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,The summer of my third year,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:45.52,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,none of my classmates \Nwere able to participate in meets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.27,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:53.37,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,what happened to that first-year\Nwas just an opportunity for me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:59.46,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,to release all my pent-up anger\Nand achieve some self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.22,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder they hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:11.11,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Because of a moment's decision,\NI wasted three years of their effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.28,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for Sakaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.28,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.92,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he hates you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.86,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder he hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:26.92,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I became unable to see anything but myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.35,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.17,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried I might do something similar again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:37.78,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I was nearly unable to stop myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:46.06,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,You've been hesitant about running\Nbecause you were worried about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:49.79,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,But you had a reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:52.15,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,A reason you had to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:56.03,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to use violence\Nagainst another person, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.45,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.53,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.75,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.43,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Before I cause any more trouble for you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.70,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.67,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.32,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,We've already started running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:22.35,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you bail on us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.81,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,They're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.27,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I'm glad to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.51,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:34.78,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,We more or less already knew that\Nyou tend to act before you speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:38.21,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I can't believe\Nyou were worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.24,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:45.17,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.66,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.69,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:53.05,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say yes when\Nyou're asked face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.49,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:02.43,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I was captivated by the way you ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.23,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I was moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.37,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe someone \Ncould have such pure running form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:13.47,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might already\Nknow the answer I was seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:18.49,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What it means to run.\NThe answer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.71,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,But I still haven't found the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:28.21,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The more I run, the more\Ndifficult I realize it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.93,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.89,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,I have fun running with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:38.34,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too. In fact, I have more fun than Jota!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.61,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.05,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,I was just speaking my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:44.22,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ruin the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.54,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.81,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:51.75,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoy running with you guys,\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:58.90,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, the goal is still far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.87,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.95,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:26.56,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is getting cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.07,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:32.12,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that concludes our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.94,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.67,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.65,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.61,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for believing in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.66,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.49,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I want to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.44,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,In the Hakone Ekiden with this team!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.64,flashback,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's aim for the top together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.64,flashback,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.58,flashback,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The Hakone Ekiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.86,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:15.77,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I'm serious about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.51,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.25,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:27.43,main,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys. Kakeru's finally\Nready to take things seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:30.52,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's serious about\Nrunning at Hakone starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.52,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.76,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we already were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:37.25,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,Then what have we been doing until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.74,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,No, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.34,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.69,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:42.67,main,NARRATION,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “You're Not Alone.”
